Notes: Jeana Hoffman's three-pointer with 5.7 seconds remaining lifts #19 South
Dakota to a 66-65 win over Wayne State.  USD snaps Wayne State's 13-game
home court win streak.  Jeana Hoffman led USD with 17 points while Teresa
Case scored 15 points for Wayne State.
